aAba sukaAtFA", "text_ar": "اَصَابَ سُكَاتًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He met with,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "experienced, a disease that prevented him from speaking."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "huwaEalaY sukaAti AlA^amori", "text_ar": "هُوَعَلَى سُكَاتِ الاَمْرِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He is at the point of accomplishing the affair."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kunotu EalaY sukaAti h`*ihi AlHaAjapi", "text_ar": "كُنْتُ عَلَى سُكَاتِ هٰذِهِ الحَاجَةِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I was at the point of attaining this want,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "needful affair."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hay~apN sukaAtN", "text_ar": "حَيَّةٌ سُكَاتٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A serpent that bites before one has knowledge of it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A, K, TA;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sakuwtN", "text_ar": "سَكُوتٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["AZ", "M", "K", "S", "A", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}